name: SELEZIONE
description:
Collage piece w/ Jp_colacioppo.
3000x3000

This is my first piece in collaboration with another artist, an amazing photographer. I really enjoyed creating this piece, analyzing and playing with his different photographs until I decided on this one.

Thank you @jp_colacioppo for giving me the opportunity to work on this piece, go see his excellent photographs and take some of his work with you.
